<lb n="0674b21" ed="T"/><note place="inline">引四十</note></p>
<lb n="0674b22" ed="T"/><p cb:type="dharani" xml:id="pT20p0674b2201">塢答波<note place="inline">二合引</note>捺演覩弭劍<note place="inline">引</note>乞叉<note place="inline">二合</note>曩訶阿
